            Website: <a href="https://capallo.co">capallo.co</a></p>
        </div>

        <h2>15. Dispute Resolution</h2>

        <p>Any disputes arising from this Privacy Policy or our data practices will be governed by the laws of Bangladesh and subject to the jurisdiction of courts in Dhaka, Bangladesh.</p>

